## 🏗️ v9.4 실전 설계: Gogs 계층형 보안 시스템

### 설계 구조: 부모-자식 노드 계층

```rust
use std::cell::RefCell;
use std::rc::{Rc, Weak};

#[derive(Debug)]
struct GogsSecurityNode {
    node_id: usize,
    security_level: usize,
    parent: RefCell<Weak<GogsSecurityNode>>,
    children: RefCell<Vec<Rc<GogsSecurityNode>>>,
}

impl GogsSecurityNode {
    fn new(node_id: usize, level: usize) -> Rc<Self> {
        Rc::new(Self {
            node_id,
            security_level: level,
            parent: RefCell::new(Weak::new()),
            children: RefCell::new(Vec::new()),
        })
    }

    fn add_child(parent: &Rc<Self>, child: Rc<Self>) {
        parent.children.borrow_mut().push(Rc::clone(&child));
        *child.parent.borrow_mut() = Rc::downgrade(parent);
    }

    fn get_parent(&self) -> Option<Rc<Self>> {
        self.parent.borrow().upgrade()
    }

    fn get_child_count(&self) -> usize {
        self.children.borrow().len()
    }

    fn get_node_info(&self) -> String {
        format!("Node {}: Level {}", self.node_id, self.security_level)
    }
}
```

### 메모리 추적 과정

```
초기 상태:
root (StrongCount: 1, WeakCount: 0)

자식 1 추가:
root (StrongCount: 1, WeakCount: 1)
  └─ child1 (StrongCount: 1, WeakCount: 0)
     parent: Weak (downgrade로 생성)

자식 2 추가:
root (StrongCount: 1, WeakCount: 2)
  ├─ child1 (StrongCount: 1, WeakCount: 0)
  └─ child2 (StrongCount: 1, WeakCount: 0)

root 스코프 종료:
→ StrongCount = 0 → 즉시 메모리 해제!
→ WeakCount가 있어도 상관없음 (삭제를 결정하지 않음)
```

